0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"ナオ","body":"パスパレはパスパレ、ビビキャンはビビキャン。\n自分たちのことだけ考えればいい。\n誰かの夢や期待なんて重荷だよ。邪魔なだけ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"angry02","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event246-03-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"邪魔って……！\nビビキャンのみんなの想いをそんなふうに言わなくても……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event246-03-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻弥","body":"そうです。ビビキャンのみなさんが\nどれだけの想いで練習してきたのか、それを一番よく知ってるのは\nナオさんじゃないですか","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"serious01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event246-03-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"ナオ","body":"知ってるからこそ言ってるんだよ。\n邪魔だし、余計な雑念にしかならない","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"angry02","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event246-03-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySo